it.csi.mddtools.guigen
Interface MapViewGadgets

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
public interface MapViewGadgets
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Map View Gadgets'.

The following features are supported:

  • Layer Switcher
  • Background Map Map Service Name
  • Background Map Switcher Label
  • Background Photo Aerial Map Service Name
  • Background Photo Aerial Switcher Label
  • Point Editing Active
  • Line Editing Active
  • Polygon Editing Active
  • Modify Editing Active

See Also:
GuigenPackage.getMapViewGadgets()
